snippet.title: Dr Kawashima's Brain Training for Nintendo Switch - Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Dr Kawashima's Brain Training for Nintendo Switch arrives on January 3rd, 2020! Get ready to challenge your brain with a variety of classic and new exercises!

Official website:
https://nintendo.co.uk/braintraining?utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=BrainTraining%7CAnnouncementTrailer%7Co2VV%7Cm_id_cd3H9Dxr8w%7Cw41
